-- Kohl's CEO to step down: paper
-- 
-- Thu Aug 21, 2008 2:31am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/08/21/us-kohls-ceo-idUSWNAB790720080821

 

 (Reuters) - Larry Montgomery is expected to step down as retailer Kohl's Corp ( KSS.N ) chief executive, The Wall Street Journal said. 

 President Kevin Mansell is taking over from Montgomery, who will remain chairman, the paper said. 
   (Reporting by  Ajay Kamalakaran  in Bangalore)